{"tid":1191844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明知果隻藥食你唔好，點解次次都食返果隻藥？","createTime":"2019-06-08T06:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T01:57:36.000Z","uid":202464,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"860e1cff074df414052daefeaabb13296e6c9324","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"呢隻藥都食左二十幾年，對病情毫無幫助，點解間藥廠仲叫人繼續食？<br />\n<br />\n因為間藥廠係做獨市生意。佢不思進取食，只諗住賺你錢。"},{"pid":"77c6212fb90c2b2ebc5357e481e4390948ff8a83","tid":1191844,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:49:38.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"8fc83a10afc12b775707a61ca33b9a7c3afffd3d","tid":1191844,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"24b9a4abf4f004df4c045da13a1830146f45de95","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"病人蠢唔使講。<br />\n<br />\n我仲見到藥廠搵好多打手想洗人腦，搞笑既係，佢地心知隻藥無效係人都知，所以都唔再吹噓隻藥有幾得。<br />\n<br />\n轉為恐嚇病人你唔幫襯佢地買呢隻藥，病人以後都無藥食。"},{"pid":"14d091cfa2abbefd004a32e5cc575635d74cc870","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:59:34.000Z","msg":"我即管睇下，有無藥廠打手入黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b65faf4181c798b42f31a925c03a7356e444011","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077117bdd847194001688c2b6dcda7bb59930f56","tid":1191844,"uid":25019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"普通感冒發燒睇醫生 次次都係個啲藥又關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a3b64dab3410c54ae55bb043bdd83956f7c2fb12","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通感冒發燒睇醫生 次次都係個啲藥又關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食得你好既，梗係繼續食。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食左二十幾年都唔好，仲食？嫌錢多？"},{"pid":"fb29a6ee77eb9aca629d5cc09f8764415c10d692","tid":1191844,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"精神科藥物係咁<br />\n要你食一世"},{"pid":"c03e97be4bd8601f9c084ba02b6f4faa8ca46290","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"如果你當果d爛鬼藥係符水、香爐灰，食左求心安既。我唔阻你。但唔好呃自己話食完會病好。"},{"pid":"9fb789ead443ae90b4fb51cb8ea0c5e54d202fb8","tid":1191844,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母關時事乜撚事"},{"pid":"d0b9232cea29f14cbf36d511dfb371fc69eda5a5","tid":1191844,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb789ead443ae90b4fb51cb8ea0c5e54d202fb8","tid":1191844,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母關時事乜撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"藥=和理非非方式示威"},{"pid":"0915848ddb08518faf93093734e9ef4ffb38574f","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母關時事乜撚事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關唔關事就睇你有無慧根啦"},{"pid":"70ce7d3c2028cc87647dc2155ed09e8fa030e507","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b52dd08419b1a3c86f2e37d2ea4c030e858ace3","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23de3a4239a54102c6c2f4da3fb1f231b71f12d7","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca3d594d427291dd4a8d6ec7e6019f6140594e9","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5d177236a1c7881f43206f43cb5e9e6fe42fd5","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"藥廠打手唔敢入黎。笑死。"},{"pid":"f344b9b44a3c34aa6bc410e22e896374a7916b2f","tid":1191844,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"其實睇公立醫院已經輸一半, 好多冷門藥佢地都無<br />\n你咁岩踩中要食冷門藥果班睇一世公立都唔會好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520f27f50b2599dc4f1462f68be208ecc324e7a6","tid":1191844,"uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"唔迫你買呢隻藥邊有錢收，你用第隻藥我就督灰比警犬"},{"pid":"590e3470df9d81f9494d0778b949094d9faa5ce2","tid":1191844,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔迫你買呢隻藥邊有錢收，你用第隻藥我就督灰比警犬</blockquote><br />\n好多港豬仲未知藥廠同病毒蛇鼠一窩互扯貓尾"}]}